OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,8,Fwas found dead in a culvert, having
OL,9,Fset off on his bicycle from his home
OL,10,Fin south Belfast on the evening of
OL,11,FSunday June 21 2020, planning to meet
OL,12,Ftwo friends in the Cavehill area in
OL,13,Fthe north of the city.
OL,15,FPSNI Detective Chief Inspector
OL,16,FPhillips became the senior
OL,17,Finvestigating officer (SIO) in
OL,18,Frelation to Noah's case on Wednesday
OL,19,F24 June 2020, when the teenager had
OL,20,Fbeen missing for three days.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FHe is the 76th witness to give
OL,8,Fevidence to the inquest which is
OL,9,Fsitting before a jury at Belfast
OL,10,FCoroners Court and is now in its 20th
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, Brenda Campbell KC,
OL,14,Frepresenting Fiona Donohoe, had
OL,15,Fquizzed Mr Phillips about police logs
OL,16,Ffrom 25 June 2020 where he outlined
OL,17,Fhis then "hypothesis" that "Noah has
OL,18,Fdisappeared of his own accord and he
OL,19,Fis either on his own or with a third
OL,20,Fparty".
OL,26,@yD@JOUyD@UO]yD@\OU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FMs Campbell posited that over the
OL,8,Fsummer of 2020 when Noah's body had
OL,9,Fbeen found this hypothesis "became the
OL,10,Fonly one".
OL,12,FShe put it to the senior officer on
OL,13,FWednesday: "The reality is that your
OL,14,Finvestigation pursued the child and
OL,15,Fnot the evidence and in adopting your
OL,16,Fhypothesis that Noah did this by
OL,17,Fchoice, you failed to find the answer."
OL,19,FMr Phillips said it was "not a
OL,20,Fquestion I can respond to".
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@IO]uD@LOUyD@gO]{D@YOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FMs Campbell continued: "You've met
OL,8,FFiona Donohoe and you've learned a lot
OL,9,Fabout her son in the course of the
OL,10,Flast six years in this inquest.
OL,12,F"And you understand the enormous
OL,13,Fprivilege and the enormous
OL,14,Fresponsibility it has been to ask so
OL,15,Fmany questions on her behalf in the
OL,16,Fcourse of this inquest.
OL,26,@oD@XOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,F"But no matter how many questions I
OL,8,Fask, at the end of this process she
OL,9,Fstill has no answer and she has to
OL,10,Flisten to you say over 30 times 'I
OL,11,Fdon't know'."
OL,13,FMr Phillips said the number was so
OL,14,Fhigh because he was asked a number of
OL,15,Fquestions "in succession" that he "can
OL,16,Fnever have an answer to", adding that
OL,17,Fhe had admitted to failings, for
OL,18,Fexample in relation to the CCTV
OL,19,Ffootage from the Northwood Drive
OL,20,Fproperty.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@MO]wD@KOUwD@YO]wD@cOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FMs Campbell said Ms Donohoe and the
OL,8,Finquest would be left without answers
OL,9,F"not because there isn't an answer".
OL,11,F"There is an answer but you failed to
OL,12,Flook for it," she said.
OL,14,FMr Phillips said: "Yes I did and I
OL,15,Fapologise for that."
OL,17,F"And you failed to find it," she said.
OL,19,FThe lead investigator replied: "Yes."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@cO]sD@AOUtD@MO]vD@SOUwD@TO]yD@
OL,26,AAOUyD@\O]{D@`OU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/16
