CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FThe inquest has previously heard Noah
OL,8,Fwas captured on CCTV leaving his home
OL,9,Fin Belfast at about 3.30am on the day
OL,10,Fhe disappeared, returning just over
OL,11,Fhalf an hour later, without his
OL,12,Fheadphones and flip flops.
OL,14,FThe footage was seized by officers in
OL,15,FJune 2020 but was not watched until
OL,16,FJanuary 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
