OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FMs Campbell referred to "all the
OL,8,Fevidential opportunities that flowed
OL,9,Ffrom" that footage and put it to Mr
OL,10,FPhillips: "Your position is 'we should
OL,11,Fhave (viewed it) but it was a note
OL,12,Fabout Fiona Donohoe's 'squeaky doors'
OL,13,Fthat give us the assurance we didn't
OL,14,Fneed it'."
OL,16,FMr Phillips said: "Yes, and I'm not
OL,17,Fputting any blame on Fiona at all, it
OL,18,Fwas an investigative failure on my
OL,19,Fpart", adding "I took the account that
OL,20,Fhe didn't leave the house because of
OL,21,Fhis obedience to rules and time".
OL,26,@oD@YOUqD@EO]rD@KOUvD@JO]xD@SOU{D@EO]{D@
OL,26,AOOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/16
