OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FShe said this included the failure to
OL,8,Fuse telelocation data to get to the
OL,9,FNorthwood Road area where the culvert
OL,10,Fis located on Sunday night or Monday,
OL,11,F"failure to identify the culvert" as a
OL,12,Fplace Noah might be, "serious delay in
OL,13,Fcommencing and the conducting the
OL,14,Fsearch of that culvert", as well as
OL,15,F"failure to deploy appropriate
OL,16,Fresources in light of that danger".
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@aO]tD@VOUvD@WO]wD@AOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FShe put it to Mr Phillips "you
OL,8,Fchallenged and you changed nothing"
OL,9,Fabout the search, to which he said
OL,10,F"no", and then "you didn't challenge
OL,11,Fand you didn't change the deployment
OL,12,Fof specialist resource".
OL,14,FMr Phillips said: "No, I asked the
OL,15,Fquestion but I didn't suggest they
OL,16,Fwere going too slowly."
OL,18,FWhen being asked about further
OL,19,Ffailings to recover CCTV footage, Mr
OL,20,FPhillips defended PSNI colleagues.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@cO]rD@AOUrD@DO]rD@POUtD@WO]vD@
OL,26,ASOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
