OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FHe said it was his job as SIO to
OL,8,F"drive the investigation to, yes,
OL,9,Fensure the information they had was
OL,10,Fcorrect and in some cases that didn't
OL,11,Fwork" and "there were some failings
OL,12,Fand I've apologised for that" but
OL,13,Fadded that is "not to say people
OL,14,Finvolved in this were incompetent,
OL,15,Fthey were good detectives for many
OL,16,Fyears".
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@EO]sD@KOUtD@]O]uD@OOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
