PN,41115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781722095
OL,3,C'Mistakes made' in Donohoe
OL,4,Cinvestigation but not deliberately,
OL,5,Cdetective says
OL,7,FHe said detectives and officers
OL,8,Finvolved in Noah's investigation have
OL,9,Fworked on "many many instances, many
OL,10,Fcrimes, other cases that have all
OL,11,Fworked out very well so, yes we made
OL,12,Fmistakes but they're not incompetent
OL,13,Findividuals".
OL,15,F"None of this was done deliberately;
OL,16,Fit was just human error," he said.
